videos.headline: Williams pushes into end zone for short UNC TD
videos.description: Javonte Williams breaks through Virginia Tech's defense and squeezes into the end zone to get the Tar Heels on the board on their first drive.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Williams pushes into end zone for short UNC TD) 2020/10/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dyami Brown shows off the nice footwork on UNC TD
videos.description: Sam Howell throws deeep to Dyami Brown, who makes an off-balance catch in the end zone for a 37-yard UNC touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Dyami Brown shows off the nice footwork on UNC TD) 2020/10/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: UNC's Williams uses acrobatic hurdling move for TD
videos.description: Javonte Williams takes off and leaps over defenders to get into the end zone for a 19-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UNC's Williams uses acrobatic hurdling move for TD) 2020/10/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mitchell walks in Virginia Tech TD
videos.description: James Mitchell takes a handoff and walks the ball into the end zone to get the Hokies on the board.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mitchell walks in Virginia Tech TD) 2020/10/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Herbert uses stiff-arm to get into the end zone
videos.description: Khalil Herbert fights off defenders and makes his way into the end zone for an 8-yard Virginia Tech touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Herbert uses stiff-arm to get into the end zone) 2020/10/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Newsome somersaults into the end zone for UNC TD
videos.description: Dazz Newsome catches a backwards pass and takes it to the house, diving into the end zone for a 6-yard UNC touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Newsome somersaults into the end zone for UNC TD) 2020/10/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Howell, Brown connect for another deep TD
videos.description: Sam Howell throws down field and finds Dyami Brown, who hauls the ball into the end zone in traffic.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Howell, Brown connect for another deep TD) 2020/10/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Carter breaks free for 16-yard TD run
videos.description: UNC's Michael Carter finds an opening and takes off into the end zone for the Tar Heels score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Carter breaks free for 16-yard TD run) 2020/10/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hendon Hooker runs it in for short Virginia Tech TD
videos.description: Virginia Tech quarterback Hendon Hooker takes it to the end zone himself to pick up a 5-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hendon Hooker runs it in for short Virginia Tech TD) 2020/10/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Herbert takes off for 52-yard TD run
videos.description: Khalil Herbert cuts back and takes the ball 52 yards to the end zone for the Hokies.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Herbert takes off for 52-yard TD run) 2020/10/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hendon Hooker finds Tayvion Robinson for 33-yard TD
videos.description: Hendon Hooker finds Tayvion Robinson, who runs into the end zone for a Hokies touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hendon Hooker finds Tayvion Robinson for 33-yard TD) 2020/10/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Newsome brushes off defenders for 12-yard score
videos.description: Dazz Newsome catches a pass from Sam Howell and fights off defenders to get into the end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Newsome brushes off defenders for 12-yard score) 2020/10/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: UNC's Carter takes it all the way with 62-yard run
videos.description: Michael Carter takes the ball all the way to the house for a 62-yard touchdown on 1st-and-25.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UNC's Carter takes it all the way with 62-yard run) 2020/10/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hooker, Mitchell link up for 26-yard score
videos.description: Hendon Hooker makes a pass into traffic and it lands in the hands of James Mitchell, who runs into the end zone for a Virginia Tech touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hooker, Mitchell link up for 26-yard score) 2020/10/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: UNC tops Virginia Tech in back-and-forth scoring battle
videos.description: UNC quarterback Sam Howell throws three touchdown passes, and the Tar Heels top the Hokies 56-45.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (UNC tops Virginia Tech in back-and-forth scoring battle) 2020/10/10 ESHEET SOTFULL
